node.descriptionp1: The Shanghai Major 2016 will be the second of the “Major Events” of Valve’s Dota Major Championships. It started with the Frankfurt Major back in 2015 that saw OG taking the first place position and Team Secret and Evil Geniuses taking second and third place respectively.
node.descriptionp2: Valve's major tournaments will end with The International 2016. The majors includes: American qualifiers, Chinese qualifiers, European qualifiers and SEA qualifiers. The main event takes place at the Mercedes-Benz Arena in Shanghai, China.
node.descriptionp3: The group stages will begin February 25th until February 28th, and the main event will be March 2nd lasting until March 6th. The following event will be the Manila Major.
